title: SPY x HERSCHEL SUPPLY
description: Herschel Supply Co. manufactures the finest quality backpacks, bags, travel goods and accessories ultimatley creating timeless product with a fine regard for detail. It's this passion to define individuality and personal style in a new way that brought us to collaborate with our friends from the North. Herschel is about our past, present and future fashion and utility; SPY is about having, experiencing and creating FUN. The combination yields a goggle and hip-pack collaboration that shall bring the rad for generations to come.
